&lt;p&gt;AcuityMD’s mission is to accelerate the adoption of cutting edge medical technology. As part of the marketing team, you’ll play a pivotal role in shaping our go-to-market strategy, testing new campaign ideas, and driving revenue. We’re not just marketing a product; we’re driving an industry-wide shift in how MedTech companies find and close their best opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our focus is on equipping Sales for success, collaborating with Product to refine and communicate our value, and working closely with customers to ensure they get the most out of our solutions. If you&#39;re looking for a fast-paced, growing, and collaborative team that makes a positive impact, AcuityMD&#39;s marketing team is the place to be.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the creation and execution of AcuityMD’s content calendar across blog, email, social, customer stories, and thought leadership programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the Head of Brand &amp;amp; Communications to translate company narrative, positioning, and market insights into compelling content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write and edit a wide range of content including articles, reports, case studies, event content, executive bylines, and customer success stories&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Flywheel and other major company events through content development before, during, and after the event&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage content production workflows and coordinate with internal subject matter experts, customers, freelancers, and agencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop content that supports demand generation campaigns and helps prospects move through the buyer journey&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Product Marketing to bring new products, features, and customer success stories to market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive content distribution across owned, earned, and social channels to maximize reach and engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Measure content performance and use data to continuously improve content quality, audience engagement, and business impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a high bar for editorial quality, consistency, and brand voice across all published content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
