&lt;h2&gt;Data Analyst | Software Engineering Track&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AcuityMD is a software and data platform that accelerates access to medical technologies. We help MedTech companies understand how their products are used, why customers vary, and identify opportunities for physicians to better serve their patients. Each year, the FDA approves ~6,000 new medical devices. Our platform helps MedTech companies get these products to physicians more effectively so they can improve patient care with the latest technology. We&#39;re backed by Benchmark, Redpoint, ICONIQ Growth, and Ajax Health.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you&#39;ll investigate customer questions about the data that powers critical business decisions while building the technical foundation for a career in software engineering. As part of our &lt;strong&gt;Software Engineering Track&lt;/strong&gt;, you&#39;ll become an expert in AcuityMD&#39;s data platform, develop advanced SQL and Python skills, learn modern AI-assisted development practices, and partner closely with experienced engineers to improve our products. Team members who demonstrate strong technical growth and engineering fundamentals will have the opportunity to transition into Junior Software Engineer roles.&lt;/p&gt;
