&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Communication&lt;/strong&gt;: Engage regularly with customers to understand their evolving needs and challenges, identifying opportunities for growth, and ensuring overall customer satisfaction. Additionally, send quarterly newsletters with company updates, including new feature launches, to keep customers informed and engaged.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Seamless Transition from Sales&lt;/strong&gt;: Work closely with the Growth Account Executive to ensure a smooth handoff of sales opportunities. Facilitate a seamless transition of account details and customer expectations to maintain continuity and customer satisfaction.&lt;/li&gt;
