&lt;li&gt;Drive user-facing product engagement and education efforts such as onboarding notifications and product tours for feature and product releases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support content marketing efforts to enable go-to-market efforts, including guides, case studies, videos, and blog posts&lt;/li&gt;
